00:00:53.346 --> 00:01:12.654
Remember, I told you this was an assignment, and they were going to use this to suppress the Second Amendment, trying to campaign on it. I saw it accelerating clear into the spring and the summer.

00:01:12.655 --> 00:01:30.599
