00:03:11.913 --> 00:03:28.271
All that is under the curse. Jesus Christ came that you might have life and have it more abundantly, in abundance to the full until it overflows.

00:03:28.272 --> 00:03:44.050
The spirit of depression and discouragement has to leave. Jesus is at the right hand of the Father making intercession for us every single day.

00:03:44.052 --> 00:03:49.158
